title: Be People Smart || EP:109
description:
Hey Rehabbers:
The most successful people have one trait in common: THEY ARE PEOPLE SMART. Relational Intelligence is a real thing that matters so much. Today's episode is going to help you become more people smart with your life. These four things will protect your life from being used and taken advantage of.

It All Starts With You.
